<div class="profile-body">
  <div class="container">
    <h3 class="mt-4">Your compatability with <a href="/{{friend._id}}">{{friend.name}}</a></h3>

    <div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm">
          <div class="card-deck friends-deck compat-deck compat-cards">
            <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
              <a href="/profile/{{req.user._id}}">
                <img class="card-img-top img-thumbnail" src="{{user.imgPath}}" alt="Card image cap">
              </a>
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title text-center">{{user.username}}</h5>
                <p class="card-text text-center">
                  <span>{{user.zodiac}}</span><br>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-sm compat-icon pt-5">
          <div>
            {{#ifEquals compatability 1}}
            <i class="fas fa-skull-crossbones fa-8x"></i>
            {{else}}
            {{/ifEquals}}

            {{#ifEquals compatability 2}}
            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle fa-8x"></i>
            {{else}}
            {{/ifEquals}}


            {{#ifEquals compatability 3}}
            <i class="fas fa-thumbs-up fa-8x"></i>
            {{else}}
            {{/ifEquals}}

            {{#ifEquals compatability 4}}
            <i class="fas fa-heart fa-8x"></i>
            {{else}}
            {{/ifEquals}}

            {{#ifEquals compatability 5}}
            <i class="fas fa-grin-hearts fa-8x"></i>
            {{else}}
            {{/ifEquals}}
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="compat-score-h3">Score</h3>
            <h1>{{compatability}}/5</h1>
          </div>

        </div>


        <div class="col-sm">
          <div class="card-deck friends-deck compat-deck compat-cards">
            <div class="card" style="width: 18rem;">
              <a href="/{{friend._id}}">
                <img class="card-img-top img-thumbnail" src="{{friend.imgPath}}" alt="Card image cap">
              </a>
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title text-center">{{friend.name}}</h5>
                <p class="card-text text-center">
                  <span>{{friend.zodiac}}</span><br>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="card card-body compat-info">
      <span class="compatability">
        <h4><span class="zodiac-compat-h4">{{user.zodiac}}</span> & <span class="zodiac-compat-h4">{{friend.zodiac}}</span></h4>
        <p class="mt-3">
          {{#ifEquals compatability 1}}
          This is a disasterous pairing. You have a hard time understanding each other, and are likely ill-prepared to
          read
          each other's reactions and moods. Miscommunication and frustration are likely down the road. Please proceed
          with
          caution.
          {{else}}
          {{/ifEquals}}

          {{#ifEquals compatability 2}}
          Hmmm this one can go either way. If you're willing to put in the effort to acquaint yourselves with each
          other's
          communication styles and idiosyncracies, you could find fulfillment in this relationship. But be wary â€”
          chances
          of
          hurt and misunderstanding are high. It can end in disaster just as easily as it could end in fulfillment.
          {{else}}
          {{/ifEquals}}

          {{#ifEquals compatability 3}}
          This is a solid match
          {{else}}
          {{/ifEquals}}

          {{#ifEquals compatability 4}}
          This is a strong match. There might be some hesitation toward getting to know each other at first, but don't
          let
          fear triumph over curiosity. You have the chance to nurture a strong connection that will be both fulfilling
          and
          joyous.
          {{else}}
          {{/ifEquals}}

          {{#ifEquals compatability 5}}
          Your star signs are as compatible as they come. You share a mutual understanding forged by complimentary
          energies.
          Whether your relationship is platonic, romantic, or otherwise, it will likely be a great source of
          fulfillment
          for
          both of you.
          {{else}}
          {{/ifEquals}}
        </p>
      </span>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<footer>
  <div>
    <small>AstroMatch 2018</small>
  </div>
</footer>